<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>E-Commerce Web Application</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        main {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: normal;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: normal;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        h3 {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: normal;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: normal;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        ol {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding-left: 0;
        }

        ul {
            list-style-type: disc;
            margin-left: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Welcome to our E-Commerce Web Application!</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section>
            <h2>Key Features:</h2>
            <ol>
                <li>
                    <h3>Product Management:</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Create:</strong> Easily add new products to our database, including details like name, description, price, and images.</li>
                        <li><strong>Edit:</strong> Update existing product information as needed, ensuring accuracy and relevance.</li>
                        <li><strong>Delete:</strong> Remove products from the database when they're no longer available or relevant.</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h3>User-friendly Interface:</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Our intuitive user interface allows customers to browse through products, add items to their cart, and proceed to checkout seamlessly.</li>
                        <li>Clear navigation and structured layouts ensure a pleasant shopping experience for users of all levels.</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h3>Responsive Design:</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Our application is built with responsiveness in mind, ensuring compatibility across various devices and screen sizes.</li>
                        <li>Whether users are accessing the platform from a desktop, laptop, tablet, or smartphone, they'll enjoy a consistent and optimized experience.</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ol>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>About Us:</h2>
            <p>We are a team of enthusiastic students and beginners passionate about software development. This project represents our dedication to learning and applying modern web technologies to solve real-world problems. We welcome feedback and suggestions for improvement as we continue to refine and enhance our application.</p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Get Started:</h2>
            <p>Explore our E-Commerce Web Application today and discover a convenient and enjoyable way to shop online. Whether you're a customer looking for quality products or an administrator managing the platform, we're here to support your needs every step of the way.</p>
            <p>Thank you for choosing our E-Commerce Web Application. Happy shopping!</p>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
